            <div class="acc-title" id="faq-q1" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faq-a1">What industries does AceTec serve? <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></div>
            <div class="acc-body" id="faq-a1" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-q1">AceTec serves the military &amp; aerospace, rail transportation, telecom &amp; networking, industrial automation, high-performance computing, and sensor simulation sectors — primarily across Korea and the broader Asia-Pacific region.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="acc-item">
            <div class="acc-title" id="faq-q2" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-a2">Do you provide custom solutions? <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></div>
